schema.description:
JSON Lines format where each line is a complete JSON object. First line: {"type":"count","total":number}. Subsequent lines: individual page objects. Example:
{"type":"count","total":150}
{"id":"uuid","name":"page1",...}
{"id":"uuid","name":"page2",...}

Note: Swagger UI may show parsing errors for streaming responses. Check Network tab in browser console for actual streaming data.
